[fireeye_helix_alerts://<name>]
instance_id = Unique identifier for Helix instance.
apikey = API Key created to retrieve alerts from Helix instance (see documentation).
api_env = Production should be use unless otherwise directed.
api_timeout = Configurable timeout in seconds (should be less than API request interval).
api_limit = Configurable limit of results to return per API request (higher limits may not complete timeout in short intervals).

[fireeye_helix_incidents://<name>]
instance_id = Unique identifier for Helix instance.
apikey = API Key created to retrieve alerts from TAP instance (see documentation).
api_env = Production should be use unless otherwise directed.
api_timeout = Configurable timeout in seconds (should be less than API request interval).
api_limit = Configurable limit of results to return per API request (higher limits may not complete timeout in short intervals).